                        <interp inst="t18690816-name-221" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE PIKE</persName>
                  </hi>. I was riding in a third-class carriage on the evening of 4th August—I was struck in the chest with a brick, which I produce—it came through the window—it did not hit me hard.</p>
